---
title: Chicken with Cranberry-Shallot Sauce plus Chili-Roasted Carrots & Mashed Potatoes
description: No matter the time of year, this homestyle meal will leave everyone thankful. You'll drizzle juicy seared chicken cutlets with a sweet and savory cranberry-shallot sauce for a harmonious blend of flavors. Serve alongside creamy, garlicky mashed potatoes and roasted carrots seasoned with Korean chili flakes for just a touch of heat.
